      <title>财务困境致 Ola Electric 股价跌破 IPO 价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/ola-electric-s-shares-slip-below-ipo-price-amid-financial-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度最大的电动滑板车制造商 Ola Electric Mobility Ltd. 的股价跌破其首次公开募股价格，这对印度今年最受关注的上市交易之一来说是一个严峻的现实考验。]]></description>
